: : Kup : :

Kup gets the comm message from Rattrap.

Kup(via comm): I am leading a team at the Ark.

Kup closes the link, and listens to Maxima.

Kup: I remember you very well from the great wars, Maxima. I know why you are really doing this. It&#39;s Megatron. However, for some reason, I believe and trust you.

He looks to his troops.

Kup: Maximals stand down.

He looks back at the Decepticon femme.

Kup: I&#39;ll leave the Ark in your care, but we&#39;ll be watching carefully.


EmprzAnastazia@... wrote:
Maxima&#39;s crimson optics glowed & narrowed. She had to pick this battle carefully.

&quot;Remove yourselves from the area!&quot; she demanded. &quot;I&#39;m willing to talk to Rodimus Prime to .. settle this arrangement!&quot; 

Her optics went to Kup. &quot;I&#39;ll speak with you, Kup! ONLY if the others back off! I don&#39;t want this place destroyed as much as you!&quot; 

With this she made her way, leaping, down to the ground then waltzing up towards Kup. Her optics caught sight of Convoy as well. This intregued her.. she hadn&#39;t seen this one before. Then her crimson optics glared at Empath. Empath was making another wrong impression with her. 

She then turned her optics on Kup as she stepped up to him. &quot;I don&#39;t wish to do anything with the inhabitants inside. I&#39;m merely protecting them.&quot; Pausing. &quot;Even though as much as I loathe your Autobot companions in stasis, my intentions are true & pure. I only want those inside to remain untouched.. & unharmed.&quot; Another pause. &quot;I&#39;ll be willing to give my life for them. I&#39;m placing my very existance on the line here, Kup. If Rodimus still sees a problem with that, then he can come to face me.&quot;

&quot;As to the others here, I believe that the Ark should have no inhabitants, but I will regularly return here. I have the Ark & Teletran 1 wired to notify me of intruders as well as Defenses armed & ready when anyone other than I are nearby. Hence, why you were fired upon. If you don&#39;t like that... then... the Ark can suffer in the future.&quot; Her voice so serious. However, she was SO bound & determined to have this her way. There was one reason as to why. & he was inside the Ark. 

Her crimson optics gazed at Kup, awaiting his response. 
